#: templates/home.html:20
msgid "Report it. Track it. Until it's fixed."
msgstr "Laporkan. Jejaki. Sehingga selesai."

#: templates/home.html:22
msgid ""
"PleaseFix is a public, community-owned issue\n"
"    tracker for Malaysia. Report local problems, follow every filing with\n"
"    every agency, and keep the issue open — together — until it is\n"
"    actually fixed."
msgstr "PleaseFix ialah penjejak isu awam milik komuniti untuk Malaysia. Laporkan masalah setempat, ikuti setiap failan dengan setiap agensi, dan pastikan isu kekal terbuka — bersama-sama — sehingga ia benar-benar selesai."

